Packages that use com.mhealthatlas.enterpriseapps.repository 
Package Description
com.mhealthatlas.enterpriseapps.command
com.mhealthatlas.enterpriseapps.command is a group of services which only mutate data but have not advanced query functionalities.
com.mhealthatlas.enterpriseapps.query
com.mhealthatlas.enterpriseapps.query is a group of services which only queries data but does not mutate them.
